# Git tracks CODE only — submitted content (entries + uploaded media) lives in
# the live store / locally, and is assembled into the static build at deploy
# ("freeze") time. One example of each is kept so the repo builds on a fresh clone.
src/content/entries/*.json
!src/content/entries/2026-06-14-example.json
public/media/*
!public/media/2026-06-14-example/
